                Image: <a href="http://www.jamesreardon.org/">James Reardon</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>Population:</b> 3,000–7,000 estimated<br/>
                <b>New Zealand status:</b> Endemic<br/>
                <b>Conservation status:</b> Threatened–Nationally Endangered<br/>
                <b>Found in:</b> Alpine and forested environments of the South Island<br/>
                <b>Threats:</b> Predation, human impacts including lead poisoning, deliberate killing, and accidents with man-made items such as cars
